projects.name: Project Starling
projects.description: A project I worked on at Google Robotics, with Catie Cuan, to create dynamic movement with large groups of robots.

projects.name: Project Music Mode
projects.description: A project I worked on at Everyday Robots. Python and Java programming used to create dynamic music on robot based arm velocities. Also created scripts to recreate music played live by robot from debug logs.

projects.name: Project SayCan
projects.description: A project I worked on at Google Robotics, gathering data and developing interfaces to improve collection pipelines for imitation learned ML models.
